<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ruler" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ruler,</orth> one that has the supreme command and power: H0A <bibl n="shak. per 5.5.30" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.291" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 291</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 105</bibl>. With <cit><quote>of:</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.1.189" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 1, 189</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.4.43" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.296" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 296</bibl>. With <cit><quote>over:</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 2, 11</bibl></cit>.
